<div class="bg-white">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative bg-gray-900 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <%= image_tag "factory.avif", class: "h-full w-full object-cover opacity-30" %>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">About Sinower</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
          Built on Experience. Positioned for Growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Journey</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600">
            Sinower USA, established in 2025, represents the next phase of our global expansion into the North American market. Our Georgia (GA) facility serves as our first official U.S. company and distribution center, marking the foundation of our long-term national development strategy.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
            While newly established in the United States, Sinower is backed by more than 20 years of manufacturing expertise and international market experience. Our manufacturing group has successfully operated across Europe and the Middle East, with established subsidiaries in France, Germany, Czech Republic, Italy, the United Kingdom, and Dubai (UAE).
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
            Over the past two decades, we have built strong operational systems, advanced production capabilities, and strict quality control standards to serve global distributors and OEM partners.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl">
          <%= image_tag "office.avif", class: "aspect-[3/2] w-full object-cover" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Product Lines Section -->
  <div class="bg-gray-50 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Core Product Lines</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:mt-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3 text-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-gray-900">Commercial Refrigeration</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600">High-performance cooling solutions for foodservice professionals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-gray-900">Commercial Cooking</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600">Durable and efficient cooking equipment built for heavy-duty use.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-gray-900">Stainless Steel Products</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600">Premium food-grade stainless steel fabrication for maximum hygiene.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Manufacturing Strength -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Manufacturing Strength & Competitive Value</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
        With vertically integrated production and efficient cost management, Sinower delivers competitive factory-direct pricing while maintaining higher build standards and consistent product reliability.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
        Our Georgia warehouse maintains sufficient inventory to ensure fast fulfillment and stable supply across the U.S. market. In addition, our factory-based engineering and technical teams provide professional support and dependable warranty service, ensuring confidence for both distributors and end users.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Expansion Plan -->
  <div class="bg-blue-600 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Strategic U.S. Expansion Plan</h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-blue-100">
          Sinower USA is committed to building a strong national footprint. Within the next three years, we plan to establish a total of nine branch offices and distribution centers across the East and West Coasts of the United States.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-blue-100">
          This expansion will enhance logistics efficiency, improve response time, and provide localized service support as we continue to grow alongside our partners.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Commitment -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Our Commitment</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
        As a fast-growing brand in the U.S. market, Sinower offers early partners the opportunity to grow together within a structured and stable distribution model.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
        We believe long-term success is built on integrity, transparency, and mutual benefit. Our goal is not only to supply equipment, but to build sustainable partnerships powered by manufacturing strength and global experience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="bg-gray-900 py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Become a Sinower Dealer</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
        Grow with a brand positioned for expansion. Sinower USA is actively building its nationwide distribution network and invites qualified dealers to grow with us.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
        <%= link_to "Contact Us Today", contact_path, class: "rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-500 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-blue-600" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
